original: Lönnqvist, Elisabet (Lisa), tandläkare, Fimspång, f. 31/5/00 i Västan-fors, Västmanl. 1., av Jacob Jacobsson o. Mina Andersscn. G. 25 m. tandl. Bnor Lönnqvist. Barn : Knut f. 38, Anders 41. — Stud:ex. i Upps. 19, tand-1 :kand. 22, tandläk. 25. Praktik i Fin-’Spång sed. 25,
translated: Lönnqvist, Elisabet (Lisa), dentist, Fimspång, b. 31/5/00 in Västanfors, Västmanl. 1st, daughter of Jacob Jacobsson and Mina Andersson. Married on the 25th with dentist Bnor Lönnqvist. Children: Knut b. 38, Anders b. 41. — Completed high school in Uppsala in 19, dental studies in 22, became a dentist in 25. Practiced in Fin’Spång from 25.
